 <title>VIAS INTRODUCTION</title>
 <link>http://boa.gov.vn/en/vias-introduction</link>
 <description>&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-dichvu-phamvi field-type-markup field-label-hidden&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-dich-vu-noi-dung-bai-viet field-type-text-long field-label-hidden&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;VIETNAM INSPECTION ACCREDITATION SCHEME (VIAS)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;Vietnam Inspection Accreditation Scheme (VIAS) is one of accreditation schemes of BoA&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
•&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;Organization and operation conform with the requirements of ISO/IEC 17011:2004&lt;br /&gt;
•&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;Assessment criteria: ISO/IEC 17020:2012 and supplementary requirements&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;
•&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;Full member and signatory of Mutual Recognition Arrangement with Asia Pacific Laboratory Accreditation Cooperation (APLAC) and International Laboratory Accreditation Cooperation (ILAC).&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;Benefit of accreditation&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
•&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;Improving management and technical performance;&lt;br /&gt;
•&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;Permission to use the accreditation stamp and logo on certificates of documents for advertisement;&lt;br /&gt;
•&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;Accredited Inspection bodies are able to be recognized by government authority to carry out inspecting commodities for government enforcement;&lt;br /&gt;
•&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;Enhancing image and competitive advantages in the domestic market and the world;&lt;br /&gt;
•&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;The customer can select the accredited inspection bodies who are independent, impartial and competent&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-makup-chia-se field-type-markup field-label-hidden&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
